these two will last until either of them decides to end it with a command
'restore_body' or either of the two leaves the realm. The target must
accept the link before it is possible to form it. Password can't be
set nor chests opened while the switch is running. The duration of the
link depends on spell %, wisdom and skill % mastery of death protection.

