wont gain any energy. The mine can't be seen by anyone except the
servants of death, i.e death knights and necromancers, who are also
immune to draining affects of the mines. Not more than one of these
mines can be placed in a room and not more than one casted by the same
knight can exist simultaneously. The mine will self-destruct if attacked
by someone, it can be attacked by anyone even if not seen.

